# Wiki.js Documentation	

# Why Wiki.js

> Wiki.js can be use for internal knowledge sharing. 

> Wiki software originated from older version control systems used for documentation and software.

> It tends to have a greater emphasis on features like access control, and document management...

> For Storage : Here , use github (https://github.com/Ashutoshlw/wiki.js-test) for store , wiki.js data will be auto fetch in 5 min interval.
{.is-success}

> Authentication: Followed documentation of wiki.js, we can use various authentication method like gmail, slack, gitlab etc...
{.is-success}

> User & Groups :  Created a group "Devops", add users in Devops groups so user can inherit properties of group.
{.is-success}

> Image upload : Image upload process is working in given instance , but there is some bugs in wiki.js 2.5.170 version , need to upgrade. 
{.is-warning}
